    • Constructor Detail

      • Request

        public Request(java.lang.String subject,
               java.lang.String description,
               Department responsibleDepartment,
               Collaborator responsibleCollaborator)

        Request

        Description: Constructs a new Request object with the specified subject, description, responsible department, and responsible collaborator. The method , by default, also sets the registration date to the current one and the status is set to pending.

        Preconditions:

        • The subject parameter must be a String.
        • The description parameter must be a String.
        • The responsibleDepartment parameter must be a Department object.
        • The responsibleCollaborator parameter must be a Collaborator object.

        Postconditions:

        • A new Request object is created with the provided subject, description, responsible department, and responsible collaborator.
        • The status of the request is set to pending.
        • The registration date of the request is set to the current date and time.
        Parameters:
        subject - The subject of the request.
        description - The description of the request.
        responsibleDepartment - The department responsible for handling the request.
        responsibleCollaborator - The collaborator responsible for the request.

    • Method Detail

      • displayStatusTypes

        public static java.lang.String displayStatusTypes()

        displayStatusTypes

        Description: Retrieves a string representation of the available status types for requests. This method retrieves the available status types using StatusType.getStatusTypes() and formats them into a string representation.

        Preconditions:

        • The StatusType class must define the getStatusTypes() method to retrieve status types.

        Postconditions:

        • A string representation of the available status types for requests is returned.
        Returns:
        A string representation of the available status types for requests.
